odelling process for a series of objects: SN2005bf, PTF2011mnb, SN2019cad,\nand SN2008D. In some cases, a decrease in the gamma ray opacity is required to\nfit the late time observations. We also discuss the other cases in which this\nscenario might be likely to explain the LC morphology.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 8 Sep 2022 17:02:11 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-11-09"}
