 and Anti-PT-symmetry breaking, dynamical magnetic phase\ntransitions, non-Hermitian skin effect, and the realization of exceptional\npoints and surfaces. Finally, we comment on some open problems in the field and\ndiscuss areas for further exploration.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 8 Sep 2022 17:42:55 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 16 Dec 2022 20:19:11 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-12-20"}
