-polar\nsequences sharing the same composition. Effectiveness of the methodology is\nverified by coarse-grained explicit-chain molecular dynamics simulations.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 8 Sep 2022 19:56:35 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 18 Oct 2022 21:55:44 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Tue, 8 Nov 2022 23:44:41 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-11-28"}
