sible\ndrivers of these waves, such as a transient driver or mode conversion of\nlongitudinal waves near the loop footpoints. In conclusion, through our\nanalysis we find that none of the commonly suspected sources proposed to drive\ndecayless oscillations in active region loops seems to be operating in this\nevent and hence, the search for that elusive wave driver needs to continue.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 9 Sep 2022 11:17:57 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-09-28"}
